(12, 2, '2012-02-16 10:01:34', '2012-02-16 10:01:34', 'This is an example of the sitemap template. The sitemap will show all the pages in your site, and arrange them in a tree-like fashion, displaying top level pages and their respective children.', 'Sitemap', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'sitemap', '', '', '2012-02-16 10:01:34', '2012-02-16 10:01:34', '', 1670, 'http://demo.cpothemes.com/illustrious/?page_id=12', 0, 'page', '', 0),
